title: Malitte
description: Sofa made up of five separable elements. When stacked together, they form single square unit. Each of five elements differently shaped to fit together, but also to make separate seating section. Sections a and c are green; b, d, and e black. Each piece covered in cotton suedecloth, with stitched reinforced edges.
name: Seating system
